com.github.fge.jsonschema.util.equivalence
Class Equivalences

java.lang.Object
  com.github.fge.jsonschema.util.equivalence.Equivalences

public final class Equivalences
extends Object

Small wrapper class over Guava's builtin Equivalences

Guava's Equivalence.equals() and Equivalence.identity() are not parameterized: this just makes them so.
